::Cheetor::

    He was going to find Primal, but he heard of the attack on the 
Cybertronian Fire. Since he was there he decided to help.
    "Cheetor MAXIMIZE!" He said standing with weapons ready.

::Primal Prime::

    He was about to tell Hot Rod about the dream, but he heard the comm about 
the attack. Transforming back to ground assult mode he headed back to the 
ship as fast as he could. Trees got in his way, but he just blasted them. 
    Soon he was at the Cybertronian Fire.
    "Prime, MAXIMIZE!" He said, not relizing that he said "Prime" instead of 
"Primal" He was standing next to Hot Rod, ready for battle, he heald his 
rifle in one hand and a sheild in the other. (The Arm things that Optimal 
Optimus has)
